    <briefdescription>
<para>GestureDetectors analyse a stream of touch events and attempt to determine the intention of the user. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>An actor is attached to a gesture detector and if the detector recognises a pattern in its analysis, it will emit a detected signal to the application.</para>
<para>This is the base class for different gesture detectors available and provides functionality that is common to all the gesture detectors.</para>
<para>@SINCE_1_0.0 <simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Gesture" kindref="compound">Gesture</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
